long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rev up your new tab with the legendary Toyota Supra! This Chrome extension brings the excitement of this iconic sports car to your browser.

The Toyota Supra live wallpaper extension showcases the sleek design and high performance of this legendary vehicle, enhancing your browsing experience with stunning visuals. Its clean interface allows you to enjoy the dynamic live wallpaper while providing essential tools for efficient navigation.

Navigate with ease using a Google search bar, quick access to customizable site shortcuts, and a clock-date display to keep you organized.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring the stunning Toyota Supra
Google Search Bar for fast and easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for your favorite websites
Clock-Date display for timely updates

Experience the thrill of the Toyota Supra every time you open a new tab! For more amazing wallpapers, visit Gameograf.com to personalize your browser.
